snippet: A 12-year-old Wisconsin girl who police say was repeatedly stabbed by two classmates trying to curry favor with a fictional horror character has been released from the hospital, the victim's parents said Friday night....

headline.print_headline: Family: Wisconsin Stabbing Victim Out of Hospital
headline.main: Family: Wisconsin Stabbing Victim Out of Hospital

lead_paragraph: A 12-year-old Wisconsin girl who police say was repeatedly stabbed by two classmates trying to curry favor with a fictional horror character has been released from the hospital, the victim's parents said Friday night.
